<plot>What Colour is Black is a documentary that follows two unique groups of children in their quest of making two separate short films. Many people in Russia think that the children with visual impairments have no future, while in India people believe that once you have cancer, your life is finished. These children will prove them wrong.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?651516</url></doc>
